libs.content:
find_program(clangtidy_exe
        names clang-tidy
        paths
            "c:/program files/llvm/bin"
            "c:/program files (x86)/llvm/bin"
    )

find_program(iwyu_exe
        names iwyu include-what-you-use
        paths
            "c:/program files/include-what-you-use/bin"
            "c:/program files (x86)/include-what-you-use/bin"
    )

deps.context: find_package(glib 2.36 required components gio gio-unix gobject)
find_package(icu 61.2 required components data i18n uc)

libs.content:
find_program(gidocgen_exe
    names gi-docgen gi-docgen.py
    hints "${cmake_source_dir}/gi-docgen/bin"
          "${cmake_source_dir}/gi-docgen"
    doc "path to the gi-docgen program"
)
